				<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
				some of the commands for all pets are<BR>
/pet attack   makes it attack whats targeted<BR>
/pet back off  makes it stop attacking <BR>
/pet sit down makes it sit <BR>
/pet stand up  makes it get up<BR>
/pet guard     makes it stay were it is a guard <BR>
/pet follow me  makes it follow you agian<BR>
/pet health report  makes it tell how much health it has<BR>
<BR>
These commands are best used if made into macro keys and put into there own hotkeys page
